{% comment %}
  FAQ Accordion — Recharge Affinity Integration
  Displays a vertically-stacked FAQ accordion with hardcoded questions and answers.
  Pure markup partial — rendered INSIDE slot templates in recharge-affinity-homepage.liquid.
  Uses .cf-faq BEM prefix to avoid CSS collision with existing .cf-did-you-know,
  .cf-dyk-footer, and .cf-articles selectors.

  Uses native <details>/<summary> elements for accordion expand/collapse without JS,
  which avoids timing issues with Recharge slot injection.

  All content is hardcoded — no metaobject definition exists for FAQ data.
{% endcomment %}

<style>
  .cf-faq {
    margin-top: 32px;
    background-color: #FFFFFF;
    padding: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cf-faq__heading {
    font-family: 'FT System', var(--font-heading--family), sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 36px;
    line-height: 47px;
    letter-spacing: -0.36px;
    color: #000000;
    margin: 0;
    padding-bottom: 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
  }

  .cf-faq__items {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .cf-faq__item {
    border-top: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
    padding-top: 24px;
    padding-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cf-faq__item:first-child {
    border-top: none;
    padding-top: 24px;
  }

  .cf-faq__item:last-child {
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .cf-faq__question {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .cf-faq__question::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .cf-faq__question-text {
    font-family: 'FT System', var(--font-body--family), sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 26px;
    letter-spacing: -0.2px;
    color: #202635;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cf-faq__chevron {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 16px;
    height: 9px;
    color: #202635;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .cf-faq__item[open] .cf-faq__chevron {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .cf-faq__answer {
    padding-top: 24px;
    max-width: 92%;
  }

  .cf-faq__answer-text {
    font-family: 'FT System', var(--font-body--family), sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 22px;
    color: #202635;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>

